# AINewsFetch-Sources

Community-maintained list of RSS/Atom news feeds for the **AI NewsFetch** iOS/macOS app.

Feeds in this list are fetched automatically by the app and merged with its built-in sources. Changes go live to all users within 24 hours — no app update required.

---

## How to contribute

### Suggest a feed (easy)
Open a [GitHub Issue](../../issues/new) with the feed name, URL, country, and city/region. The maintainer will verify and add it.

### Submit a pull request
1. Fork this repo
2. Edit `sources.json` — add your entry to the `sources` array
3. Verify the feed URL is live (paste it into a browser or RSS reader)
4. Open a pull request with a brief description

PRs are reviewed before merging. Feeds that return valid RSS/Atom and aren't paywalled/bot-blocked will generally be accepted.

---

## JSON format

Each entry in the `sources` array:

```json
{
  "name": "Some Local Paper",
  "url": "https://somelocalsite.com/feed",
  "type": "independent",
  "country": "AU",
  "state": "Victoria",
  "city": "Geelong",
  "weight": 0.65
}
